statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE visitor_id = 12345
SELECT timestamp, page_visited FROM website_traffic ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT DISTINCT visitor_id FROM website_traffic
SELECT page_visited, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic GROUP BY page_visited ORDER BY visit_count DESC
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE event_type = 'click'
SELECT website_id, visitor_id, timestamp, page_visited, event_type FROM website_traffic WHERE website_id = 1 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT website_id, visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS num_visits FROM website_traffic GROUP BY website_id ORDER BY num_visits DESC
SELECT page_visited, COUNT(*) AS num_visits FROM website_traffic WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2021-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2021-12-31 23:59:59' GROUP BY page_visited ORDER BY num_visits DESC
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(DISTINCT page_visited) AS unique_pages_visited FROM website_traffic GROUP BY visitor_id ORDER BY unique_pages_visited DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT website_id, COUNT(DISTINCT visitor_id) AS unique_visitors FROM website_traffic WHERE event_type = 'click' GROUP BY website_id ORDER BY unique_visitors DESC
SELECT id, user_id, page_visited, visit_time FROM website_traffic WHERE user_id = 1234;
SELECT * FROM user_behavior WHERE user_id = 5678 ORDER BY action_time DESC;
SELECT action_taken, COUNT(*) AS action_count FROM user_behavior GROUP BY action_taken;
SELECT page_visited FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_time >= '2022-01-01' AND visit_time <= '2022-01-31';
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_visits FROM website_traffic GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_visits > 5;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE user_id = 15 ORDER BY visit_time DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT page_visited, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-01-31 23:59:59' GROUP BY page_visited ORDER BY visit_count DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, action_taken, action_time FROM user_behavior WHERE action_time >= '2022-02-01' AND action_time < '2022-03-01' ORDER BY action_time DESC LIMIT 20;

SELECT user_id, AVG(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, visit_time, action_time)) AS avg_time_spent FROM website_traffic JOIN user_behavior ON website_traffic.user_id = user_behavior.user_id GROUP BY user_id HAVING avg_time_spent > 60;

SELECT event_name, page_name, event_time FROM events INNER JOIN pages ON events.page_id = pages.page_id WHERE events.event_time < '2022-06-01';
